area however you want.`}<br parentName="p"></br>{`
`}{`Note that the component will set the parent's `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`position`}</inlineCode>{` style to `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`relative`}</inlineCode>{` and can also adjust its own border to
match the one of the parent.`}</p>

